OL,3,CCast announced for new Bergerac series
OL,5,FThe cast of the re-imagined Bergerac
OL,6,Fseries has been announced by UKTV.
OL,8,FIrish actor Damien Molony takes on the
OL,9,Fleading role of Jim Bergerac - he has
OL,10,Fpreviously appeared in BBC shows such
OL,11,Fas Brassic and The Split.
OL,13,FDamien says: "I'm incredibly excited
OL,14,Fto be stepping into the role ... John
OL,15,FNettles has left an incredible legacy
OL,16,Fwith big shoes to fill, and I hope I
OL,17,Fcan bring a fresh take on this iconic
OL,18,Fcharacter".
