OL,5,FElsewhere, he will be joined by Zoe
OL,6,FWanamaker - perhaps best known for her
OL,7,Fappearances in My Family and Harry
OL,8,FPotter - as well as Philip Glenister
OL,9,Fof Life on Mars.
OL,11,FRather than a new storyline for each
OL,12,Fepisode, the 'contemporary twist' will
OL,13,Fsee one mystery run across each of the
OL,14,Fsix episodes in the series.
