OL,3,CCast announced for new Bergerac series
OL,5,FVisit Jersey have put their support
OL,6,Fbehind the show, with its head Tricia
OL,7,FWarwick saying: "For many, the words
OL,8,F'Jersey' and 'Bergerac' are
OL,9,Fsynonymous, and we are delighted for
OL,10,Fthe iconic TV series to return to our
OL,11,Fisland's beautiful shores.
OL,13,F"The modern re-imaging presents an
OL,14,Fopportunity to celebrate the show's
OL,15,Flegacy in Jersey, whilst reaching a
OL,16,Fnew generation of fans who will be
OL,17,Feager to 'jet set' to the featured
OL,18,Flocations".
